forum.message: You're meant to have fun in life. Now, we're going to fluff this cloud. Maybe there's a happy little bush that lives right there. I'm sort of a softy, I couldn't shoot Bambi except with a camera. Look around, look at what we have. Beauty is everywhere, you only have to look to see it. If what you're doing doesn't make you happy - you're doing the wrong thing. Don't be bashful drop me a line.

Poor old tree. Very easy to work these to death. Didn't you know you had that much power? You can move mountains. You can do anything. It's a good way of getting rid of all your anxieties and hostilities. Happy painting, God bless.
